'''自相分争之家演说（{{lang-en|The House Divided Speech}}'''）是后来担任[[美国总统|美国总统]]的[[亚伯拉罕·林肯|亚伯拉罕·林肯]]于1858年6月16日接受了伊利诺伊州共和党的[[美国参议院|美国参议员]]竞选提名后，在[[斯普林菲尔德_(伊利诺伊州)|斯普林菲尔德]]的[[舊州議會大廈遺址|伊利诺伊州议会大厦]]发表的演讲。对林肯的提名是这次共和党大会的最后一项事务，会议随后中断，进行晚餐，晚上8点再次开会。林肯是晚上会议的唯一演讲者。他的演说立即全文刊登在报纸<ref>{{Cite news|title=Conclusion of the Republican State Convention. Speech of Hon. Abraham Lincoln|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=June 19, 1858|page=2|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/20998823/lincolns_house_divided_speech/|accessdate=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220124641/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/20998823/lincolns_house_divided_speech/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|title=Republican principles. Speech of Hon. Abraham Lincoln, of Illinois, at the Republican state Convention, June 16, 1858|work=[[New-York_Tribune|New-York Tribune]]|date=June 24, 1858|page=3|via=[[newspapers.com|newspapers.com]]|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/11811421/newyork_tribune/|accessdate=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220093615/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/11811421/newyork_tribune/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|title=Speech of Hon. Abraham Lincoln|work=[[Alton_Weekly_Telegraph|Alton Weekly Telegraph]] ([[Alton,_Illinois|Alton, Illinois]])|date=June 24, 1858|page=2|via=[[newspapers.com|newspapers.com]]|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/40906336/alton_weekly_telegraph/|accessdate=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220094336/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/40906336/alton_weekly_telegraph/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、小册子<ref>{{Cite book|title=Speech of Hon. Abram [sic] Lincoln before the Republican state convention, June 16, 1858|year=1858|oclc=2454620|first=Abraham|last=Lincoln|authorlink=Abraham Lincoln}}</ref>、以及会议记录上。<ref name="Proceedings">{{Cite book|title=Proceedings of the Republican state convention, held at Springfield, Illinois, June 16th, 1858|year=1858|url=https://archive.org/details/proceedingsofr00repu/page/n7/mode/1up|location=[[Springfield,_Illinois|Springfield, Illinois]]}}</ref> 这是他争夺[[史蒂芬·阿諾·道格拉斯|斯蒂芬·道格拉斯]]的参议员席位的起点。这场竞选活动将随着[[林肯与道格拉斯的辩论|林肯-道格拉斯辩论]]达到高潮。当林肯收集并发表与道格拉斯的辩论作为他[[1860年美国总统选举|1860年总统竞选]]一部分时，他加上了相关的演讲作为前序，“自相分争之家”演说被选为开篇。 <ref>{{Cite book|title=Political Debates between Hon. Abraham Lincoln and Hon. Stephen A. Douglas, In the Celebrated Campaign of 1858, in Illinois; including the preceding speeches of each, at Chicago, Springfield, etc.; also, the two great speeches of Mr. Lincoln in Ohio, in 1859, as carefully prepared by the reporters of each party, and published at the times of their delivery|location=[[Columbus,_Ohio|Columbus, Ohio]]|publisher=Follett, Foster and Company|year=1860|url=https://archive.org/details/politicaldebate03douggoog|first=Abraham|last=Lincoln|pages=[https://archive.org/details/politicaldebate03douggoog/page/n191 1]–5|authorlink=Abraham Lincoln|first2=Stephen A.|last2=Douglas|authorlink2=Stephen A. Douglas}}</ref>

林肯的演说描绘了因为[[美國奴隸制度|奴隶制]]造成的[[美利堅聯盟國|分裂]]的危机，使[[美國北部|北部的]]共和党人团结起来。该演说与[[蓋茲堡演說|葛底斯堡演说]]和[[亚伯拉罕·林肯的第二次就职演说|第二任就职演说]]一起，是林肯职业生涯中最著名的演说之一。它以下列最著名的段落开头：<ref>{{Cite book|last=Foner|first=Eric|title=The Fiery Trial: Abraham Lincoln and American Slavery|url=https://archive.org/details/fierytrialabraha0000fone|year=2010|isbn=978-0-393-06618-0|pages=[https://archive.org/details/fierytrialabraha0000fone/page/99 99]–100}}</ref>

